SUMMARY: DELIVERY OPTIONS: The store offers home delivery, parcel shop delivery, and in-store pickup. Home delivery is handled by Česká pošta, Zásilkovna, and GLS. Parcel shop delivery is available via Zásilkovna. In-store pickup is possible at their Brno location. PRICING: Home delivery starts at 89 Kč. Parcel shop delivery starts at 55 Kč. In-store pickup is free. Free shipping is available for all orders over 2,500 Kč. A cash on delivery (COD) surcharge of 25 Kč applies to shipped orders. DISPATCH TIME: Orders are dispatched within 2 working days after payment is received. NOTABLE FEATURES: The pricing for Zásilkovna services is tiered based on package weight (up to 5kg and up to 15kg). WEBSITE ASSESSMENT: The shipping information is presented in a clear table, making it easy to compare prices. However, it lacks specific delivery timeframes (only dispatch time is provided), and there is no information on express or weekend delivery. The distinction between parcel shops and parcel lockers is not made.
